  "content": "<div class=\"mceNonEditable problem-description-box\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable firstMceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"*问题描述\"> <a id=\"menu1\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"问题描述\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"problem-description\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>6.10.0R2升级到6.11.1R1，升级失败回滚， 回滚失败， 报错：回滚失败，回滚数据库配置失败。错误码 0xB300000C</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_static/202511/ad395764c8e911f084e6fa163e0bdd14.png\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"告警信息\"> <a id=\"menu2\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"告警信息\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>回滚失败，回滚数据库配置失败。错误码 0xB300000C</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"有效排查步骤\"> <a id=\"menu3\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"有效排查步骤\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>1 检查后台 /sf/log/today/update.log</p>\n<p>搜索关键字&nbsp; fail_slow_domain_mp&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>有如下报错信息：</p>\n<p>搜索关键字： rollback vn MP database table fail_slow_domain_mp column type failed</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_static/202511/46d3bed8c8ea11f084e6fa163e0bdd14.png\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"根因\"> <a id=\"menu4\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"根因\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>客户回滚了2次，第1次回滚，已经将fail_slow_domain_mp表回滚至低版本，&nbsp;</p>\n<p>第2次又进行了一次回滚， 回滚代码发现该表的结果和代码不一致，于是回滚报错</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable problem-description-box\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"*解决方案\"> <a id=\"menu5\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"解决方案\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"problem-description\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>手动清空fail_slow_domain_mp表内容：</p>\n<p>ssh mysql-master</p>\n<p>container_exec -n pl&nbsp; &nbsp; #pl容器进不去的时候进asv容器 &nbsp;container_exec -n asv-c</p>\n<p>mysql --login-path=root</p>\n<p>use network;</p>\n<p>delete from fail_slow_domain_mp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>清空表内容后，重新再回滚即可</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"操作影响范围\"> <a id=\"menu6\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"操作影响范围\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">属于恢复操作</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"是否是临时解决方案\"> <a id=\"menu7\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"是否是临时解决方案\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">否</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"建议与总结\"> <a id=\"menu8\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"建议与总结\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mceNonEditable\"><input class=\"mceNonEditable\" style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #28282b; margin: 30px 0 10px 0; line-height: 27px; background: transparent; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border: none; user-select: none; outline: none; width: 100%;\" readonly=\"readonly\" type=\"text\" value=\"排查内容\"> <a id=\"menu9\" style=\"width: 0!important; padding: 0;\" data-text=\"排查内容\" data-anchor=\"catalogue\"></a>\n<div class=\"\" style=\"min-height: 40px;\" contenteditable=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>",
